item.description: Join members and friends of the Wedeln Ski & Outdoors club for a night of drinks and dancing to the tunes of Project DCQ, the cover band that has rocked the Wedeln Open Golf Tournament two years in a row. There's no cover charge, and it's a casual atmosphere. The Chickenbone has great food too, if you happen to come hungry! This is a great opportunity to get to know Wedeln if you're not already familiar with us, and a perfect way to wrap up the work week! The more the merrier!
item.how_to_find_us: We'll try to set up shop at a table near the stage
item.name: Wedeln & Project DCQ at The Chickenbone, Framingham
